{"type": "article", "id": 3034, "title": "碳纤维轮椅", "description": "", "date": "2014-10-24T07:38:25Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 5, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232959PHlGc50vpFOQL4mz.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tAndrew slorance 14 岁的时候患上脊椎损伤，由于传统轮椅的造型与舒适感都有问题，从那时开始他就梦想着要自己设计一个轮椅。经过多年的充分准备， Andrew slorance 终于推出了他自己的轮椅设计作品 Carbon Black 。这款轮椅采用碳纤维与皮革材质，并且重新设计了轮椅结构，一改过去传统轮椅难看而突兀的造型，展现出如同艺术品一般的气质。当然，Carbon Black 在功能上也有很大改进，改良后的结构让轮椅本身更加轻巧结实，同时，可拆卸的设计让用户出门时可以轻易地将轮椅放在后备箱内。此外，Carbon Black 还在底部搭载灯光，即使光线昏暗，也能拥有不错地路面视野。定价 1200 英镑，<a href=\"http://www.carbonblacksystem.com/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试联系购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232956GP057FbYC9rhdiOR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232957VDgZ5WSTqM3dIyYN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232957i8359frIJeWUjvXA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052329582eOvdPW9NynXUMI0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232958LGTHltgKcCZn8VSw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}